<p style="margin: 0 0 16px 0; font-size: 16px;">Hello!</p>

<p style="margin: 0 0 24px 0; font-size: 16px; color: #333333;">We received a request to reset your password for your <strong>What Am I Watching?</strong> account. If you made this request, click the button below to reset your password:</p>

<table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" width="100%" style="margin: 30px 0;">
  <tr>
    <td align="center">
      <table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">
        <tr>
          <td style="background-color: #007bff; border-radius: 6px;">
            <%= link_to "Reset My Password", @reset_url, style: "display: inline-block; padding: 14px 32px; background-color: #007bff; color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 6px; font-weight: 600; font-size: 16px;" %>
          </td>
        </tr>
      </table>
    </td>
  </tr>
</table>

<p style="margin: 24px 0 16px 0; font-size: 14px; color: #666666;">This link will expire in 2 hours for security reasons.</p>

<p style="margin: 16px 0 24px 0; font-size: 14px; color: #666666;">If you did not request this password reset, please ignore this email.</p>

<table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" width="100%" style="margin-top: 30px; padding-top: 20px; border-top: 1px solid #e0e0e0;">
  <tr>
    <td align="center" style="padding: 0;">
      <p style="margin: 0 0 8px 0; font-size: 12px; color: #666666;">If the button doesn't work, copy and paste this link into your browser:</p>
      <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 12px;">
        <a href="<%= @reset_url %>" style="color: #007bff; text-decoration: none; word-break: break-all;"><%= @reset_url %></a>
      </p>
    </td>
  </tr>
</table>